---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Manufacturing Operations Dashboard | Case Study"
  description="How real-time operations visibility reduced production delays by 28% for a UK manufacturer."
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-blue bg-brand-blue-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Demo Project</span>
        <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-slate-light">Dashboards</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate">Manufacturing Operations Dashboard</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-light">
        Real-time operations visibility replacing manual reporting, enabling proactive issue resolution.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
          <strong>Note:</strong> This is a demo project illustrating typical dashboard outcomes. Results vary by data quality and implementation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-light">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate">The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          A mid-sized manufacturer had no real-time visibility into production. The Operations Director started each day not knowing what had actually happened overnight.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Production data locked in disparate systems</li>
          <li>Daily reports prepared manually, often delayed</li>
          <li>Problems discovered hours or days after they occurred</li>
          <li>No single source of truth for KPIs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">The Solution</h2>
        <p>
          We built a real-time operations dashboard connecting to production systems:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Live production metrics updated every 15 minutes</li>
          <li>Exception-based alerts for issues requiring attention</li>
          <li>Historical trend analysis for pattern identification</li>
          <li>Mobile-friendly design for floor access</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Typical Results</h2>
        <div class="not-prose grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-success">28%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-light mt-1">Reduction in production delays</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-success">Real-time</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-light mt-1">Visibility vs. next-day reports</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Key Takeaways</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Start with the decisions people need to make, not the data available</li>
          <li>Alerts should be actionable, not just informational</li>
          <li>Adoption requires designing for actual workflows</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Ready for dashboards that work?"
    description="Book a discovery call to discuss your reporting challenges."
  />
</BaseLayout>
